data.description: NO HOA and NO CDD!! This home is ideal for entertaining and multi-generational living, offering 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, including 3 en-suites, and a Large Open-concept living area. With a Living Room/Dining Room combo, Lots of ELBOW ROOM, and Plenty of STORAGE. Breakfast bar seating, stainless steel appliances, and Large 12' deep walk in Pantry. Large .43 acre yard has fenced in back yard, 12'x24' detached carport, and 16'x22' WORKSHOP in addition to the 2 car attached garage. ROOF in 2013 and Both AC's 2019. Enjoy the mild Florida climate while entertaining friends in the 13'x15' screen enclosed lanai. Centrally located only 45 minutes to Orlando attractions, Tampa or Ocala. Less than 15 minutes from nearly 100,000 acres of state recreation lands offering camping, hiking, and hunting. Only 10 minutes from Silver Lake state recreation area which offers canoeing, boating, camping, and fishing. Only 4 miles to shopping, restaurants, and easy I-75 access at exit 301.
